{
  "stem": "23742.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And shortly after that, 12 men in my squad were instructed to report to the medical room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were to have inoculations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We weren't told why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They just said, well, you know, you're going to need this in the near future.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the following day, the 12 of us, we loaded six trucks with radio equipment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were told we were going up to a place called Bergen-Belsen in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And at that time, the name didn't mean anything to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The journey took about six hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And as we neared our destination, we noticed a very strange smell in the atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We just couldn't decide what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It wasn't a gas because we-- we-- it definitely wasn't a wartime gas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was something much stronger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We later found out it was chlorine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And as we approached the-- we didn't know what to expect.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We got to-- we saw signs on the road which said, forbidden area, military area, keep out, typhus.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then we realized we were getting into something quite, quite serious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The military police directed us to the, a parking place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were told to report to the camp commander.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was a barbed wire area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the gates were open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were watchtowers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were unmanned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we walked through the gates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the sight was quite devastating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] they were walking about in these striped uniform, those who could walk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were walking skeletons, dreadful conditions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were people laying around on the ground in grotesque situations, grotesque positions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was, it was totally unexpected.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We hadn't prepared for this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we just stood there, unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It just, it just didn't, just didn't seem possible.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
